    "description": "<p>SINENERGY PTE. LTD. is a Singapore based company that specializes in solar energy development and M&E works. With support from parent group & its business partners from other Asian countries, we leverage our past experience & technical expertise for providing cost effective timely solutions that guarantees maximum efficiency and performance to meet our clients' need across South East Asia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Sinenergy, we have built significant in-house capacity in various facets of project development and managemet such as technical, legal, regulatory, environmental and financial. With our team of skilled specialists, we are committed to harness the power of sun at commercial & domestic level through powerful, proven and cutting edge solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n </p>\r\n",
